[
  {
    "start": "0",
    "end": "23000"
  },
  {
    "text": "Businesses must make money for",
    "start": "30",
    "end": "1919"
  },
  {
    "text": "shareholders.",
    "start": "1920",
    "end": "2758"
  },
  {
    "text": "It doesn't follow that.",
    "start": "2760",
    "end": "3689"
  },
  {
    "text": "That's the purpose of a business.",
    "start": "3690",
    "end": "5999"
  },
  {
    "text": "What's the ethics of capitalism?",
    "start": "6000",
    "end": "8279"
  },
  {
    "text": "What's the responsibility",
    "start": "8280",
    "end": "10139"
  },
  {
    "text": "of companies?",
    "start": "10140",
    "end": "11159"
  },
  {
    "text": "How do we deal with global warming?",
    "start": "11160",
    "end": "13379"
  },
  {
    "text": "We can't separate business and",
    "start": "13380",
    "end": "15209"
  },
  {
    "text": "ethics anymore.",
    "start": "15210",
    "end": "16320"
  },
  {
    "start": "23000",
    "end": "60000"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm Ed Freeman, university",
    "start": "23430",
    "end": "25429"
  },
  {
    "text": "professor at the University of",
    "start": "25430",
    "end": "27109"
  },
  {
    "text": "Virginia at the Darden School.",
    "start": "27110",
    "end": "29689"
  },
  {
    "text": "I started thinking about the",
    "start": "29690",
    "end": "31039"
  },
  {
    "text": "relationship between business and",
    "start": "31040",
    "end": "32298"
  },
  {
    "text": "society 45 years",
    "start": "32299",
    "end": "34279"
  },
  {
    "text": "ago, as I was trying to understand",
    "start": "34280",
    "end": "36259"
  },
  {
    "text": "really what business was about.",
    "start": "36260",
    "end": "37759"
  },
  {
    "text": "We desperately need a new",
    "start": "39560",
    "end": "41659"
  },
  {
    "text": "story, a new narrative about",
    "start": "41660",
    "end": "43399"
  },
  {
    "text": "business.",
    "start": "43400",
    "end": "44359"
  },
  {
    "text": "The old narrative about business,",
    "start": "44360",
    "end": "45979"
  },
  {
    "text": "that business is about the money,",
    "start": "45980",
    "end": "48619"
  },
  {
    "text": "and it's about making money for",
    "start": "48620",
    "end": "49878"
  },
  {
    "text": "shareholders has a",
    "start": "49880",
    "end": "51739"
  },
  {
    "text": "hold on us, and we need",
    "start": "51740",
    "end": "53629"
  },
  {
    "text": "to give that up.",
    "start": "53630",
    "end": "54499"
  },
  {
    "text": "Look, every business",
    "start": "54500",
    "end": "56779"
  },
  {
    "text": "has always created value",
    "start": "56780",
    "end": "59119"
  },
  {
    "text": "for customers, for suppliers,",
    "start": "59120",
    "end": "61489"
  },
  {
    "start": "60000",
    "end": "95000"
  },
  {
    "text": "for employees, for communities",
    "start": "61490",
    "end": "64159"
  },
  {
    "text": "and the people that",
    "start": "64160",
    "end": "66199"
  },
  {
    "text": "put up the money.",
    "start": "66200",
    "end": "67879"
  },
  {
    "text": "Business is about",
    "start": "67880",
    "end": "69858"
  },
  {
    "text": "the interdependence",
    "start": "69860",
    "end": "71959"
  },
  {
    "text": "of these groups, the interdependence",
    "start": "71960",
    "end": "74298"
  },
  {
    "text": "of stakeholders.",
    "start": "74300",
    "end": "75709"
  },
  {
    "text": "In fact, I'd venture to say",
    "start": "75710",
    "end": "77899"
  },
  {
    "text": "the amount of money you can make",
    "start": "77900",
    "end": "79819"
  },
  {
    "text": "is a function",
    "start": "79820",
    "end": "81798"
  },
  {
    "text": "of how you deal with those",
    "start": "81800",
    "end": "83659"
  },
  {
    "text": "other stakeholders, and",
    "start": "83660",
    "end": "85819"
  },
  {
    "text": "that interdependence is",
    "start": "85820",
    "end": "88219"
  },
  {
    "text": "what makes great companies.",
    "start": "88220",
    "end": "89659"
  },
  {
    "text": "But that's not the only thing that",
    "start": "91370",
    "end": "93019"
  },
  {
    "text": "business does. Business is a",
    "start": "93020",
    "end": "94608"
  },
  {
    "text": "societal institution.",
    "start": "94610",
    "end": "96709"
  },
  {
    "start": "95000",
    "end": "132000"
  },
  {
    "text": "Since the global financial crisis,",
    "start": "96710",
    "end": "99048"
  },
  {
    "text": "we've had a renaissance of people",
    "start": "99050",
    "end": "101059"
  },
  {
    "text": "thinking about what's the, what's",
    "start": "101060",
    "end": "102889"
  },
  {
    "text": "the ethics of capitalism,",
    "start": "102890",
    "end": "104839"
  },
  {
    "text": "what's the responsibility",
    "start": "104840",
    "end": "106729"
  },
  {
    "text": "of companies, how do we deal with",
    "start": "106730",
    "end": "108679"
  },
  {
    "text": "global warming?",
    "start": "108680",
    "end": "109519"
  },
  {
    "text": "How do we deal with inequality?",
    "start": "109520",
    "end": "111559"
  },
  {
    "text": "How do we deal with gender and",
    "start": "111560",
    "end": "113449"
  },
  {
    "text": "race discrimination?",
    "start": "113450",
    "end": "115069"
  },
  {
    "text": "And that kind of perfect storm",
    "start": "115070",
    "end": "117229"
  },
  {
    "text": "has led us, has led a lot of folks",
    "start": "117230",
    "end": "119119"
  },
  {
    "text": "to say that business is just about",
    "start": "119120",
    "end": "120979"
  },
  {
    "text": "the money, doesn't",
    "start": "120980",
    "end": "122889"
  },
  {
    "text": "doesn't really work anymore.",
    "start": "122890",
    "end": "124999"
  },
  {
    "text": "It's sad to be a part of the",
    "start": "125000",
    "end": "127039"
  },
  {
    "text": "solution.",
    "start": "127040",
    "end": "128040"
  },
  {
    "text": "There are lots of ways to start,",
    "start": "129889",
    "end": "131719"
  },
  {
    "text": "but the best way to start is to",
    "start": "131720",
    "end": "133429"
  },
  {
    "start": "132000",
    "end": "163000"
  },
  {
    "text": "figure out what your purpose is.",
    "start": "133430",
    "end": "135618"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you have a sense of purpose,",
    "start": "135620",
    "end": "138139"
  },
  {
    "text": "then that will tell you",
    "start": "138140",
    "end": "140179"
  },
  {
    "text": "what issues you work on.",
    "start": "140180",
    "end": "142758"
  },
  {
    "text": "We can't separate business and",
    "start": "142760",
    "end": "144618"
  },
  {
    "text": "ethics anymore.",
    "start": "144620",
    "end": "146299"
  },
  {
    "text": "And so the idea that you have",
    "start": "146300",
    "end": "148249"
  },
  {
    "text": "business on the one hand and",
    "start": "148250",
    "end": "150109"
  },
  {
    "text": "ethics on the other is part",
    "start": "150110",
    "end": "151939"
  },
  {
    "text": "of the old story, and that",
    "start": "151940",
    "end": "153799"
  },
  {
    "text": "we have to do away with that",
    "start": "153800",
    "end": "156259"
  },
  {
    "text": "business and ethics have to be",
    "start": "156260",
    "end": "157728"
  },
  {
    "text": "integrated.",
    "start": "157730",
    "end": "158730"
  }
]